description: I am 24 living in Cavite, PH. I am single and came from a not good relationship. I'm looking for unconditional love from a good man. Someone who is family oriented. I want someone who will support each other's interest. Someone who is a Christian who takes his relationship with God very seriously. Needs to be a nonsmoker. Most importantly, loves me even with all my imperfections. I'm looking for a partner for life. Someone I can enjoy life with together.
